{"tid":1285690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"報警的權利","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:31:05.000Z","uid":265980,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33b24c4a187fa3fa456644ed7a37d1ed95761abf","tid":1285690,"uid":265980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"的警察成日叫人有咩咁叻唔好報警唔好搵佢地<br />\n<br />\n第一 我想講 佢地係有出糧 唔係做義工 <br />\n只要係工作範圍 唔到佢地選擇工作項目<br />\n<br />\n第二 作為市民 我地係有報警權利<br />\n當中包括但唔限於以下情景：<br />\n1. 唔記得帶鎖匙但懷疑自己冇熄火（當然你突然醒起搵返鎖匙或者記錯冇煮緊野你係冇犯法既，只要你報警個刻，你確信自己冇鎖匙或冇熄火）<br />\n2. 屋企唔見左野（真人真事，有人試過唔見左胸圍都報警，但警察都有責任協助你尋回，因為你確信係唔見，係有可能有人黎偷）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家遇到懷疑罪案同意外都要第一時間報警求助呀，一定唔好因爲怕事怕麻煩就唔報呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡下自己權利責任同義務！"},{"pid":"df24ec1e7be001d25dc324b6de01dec7f29e4640","tid":1285690,"uid":41803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f667796b3ca38175cdf50032ba9c38505adec7e","tid":1285690,"uid":265980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df24ec1e7be001d25dc324b6de01dec7f29e4640","tid":1285690,"uid":41803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"大家有事先報警呀<br />\n唔好亂打999<br />\n係犯法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40b69424c6368ea01be65563672b5eaee1f9ac6","tid":1285690,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpj7H2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqpj7H2.gif&h=de954cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oB5zb9J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoB5zb9J.gif&h=442e1d2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\